{"type":null,"faqId":7231,"title":"安装驱动方法","answer":"<p>1. 将手机USB 调试打开<br />2. 在U8800+手机的&ldquo;主菜单?设置 ? 应用程序 ? 开发&rdquo;界面，勾选&ldquo;USB 调试 &rdquo;选项。<br />3. 手机插入到PC 机中，会提示&ldquo;发现新硬件&rdquo;，选择&ldquo;否，暂时不&rdquo;，将驱动文件的位置指定到driver\\drivers\\adb_driver 路径即可，也可以将这个路径中的文件全部拷贝到计算机中备用。<br />4. 将手机的USB 状态调整正确之后将手机插入PC 中，会出现发现新硬件向导，请按照如下图方式进行选择操作：<br />图方式进行选择操作：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" width=\"473\" height=\"340\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/0-111026171829.PNG\" /><img style=\"WIDTH: 473px; HEIGHT: 338px\" alt=\"\" width=\"467\" height=\"338\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/1-111026171836.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>5. 到这一步的时候选择autorun 虚拟光驱中的adb_driver 这一级，选择&ldquo;确定&rdquo;</p>\n<p><img style=\"WIDTH: 563px; HEIGHT: 375px\" alt=\"\" width=\"948\" height=\"420\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/2-111026171852.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>6. 之后安装过程中可能还会出现寻找相关文件的对话框， 请将位置选择到driver\\drivers\\adb_driver 文件夹或者driver\\drivers\\adb_driver\\i386 文件夹，直到所有文件安装成功，安装成功之后出现如下画面</p>\n<p><img style=\"WIDTH: 526px; HEIGHT: 390px\" alt=\"\" width=\"891\" height=\"640\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/3-111026171917.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>安装完成手机驱动并且将U8800+手机设置为正确状态之后，在手机连接PC 的状态下，请确认PC 机已经有和手机进行通讯的必备的adb 端口。<br />在&ldquo;我的电脑&rdquo;上点击右键，选择属性，之后查看&ldquo;设备管理器&rdquo;，如果有adb 端口的话即证明U8800+手机驱动安装成功。</p>\n<p><img style=\"WIDTH: 272px; HEIGHT: 338px\" alt=\"\" width=\"336\" height=\"413\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/4-111026173117.PNG\" /><img style=\"WIDTH: 617px; HEIGHT: 381px\" alt=\"\" width=\"884\" height=\"486\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/5-111026173126.PNG\" /></p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":1,"unUseful":24,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7371","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1319617903000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":10989,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":52,"times":13,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"3","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":4.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}